workflow:
apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: dependency-workflow-23-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getuserid
        template: getuserid
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: username
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.username }}'
      - name: playlistname2id
        template: playlistname2id
        dependencies:
        - getuserid
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: playlist_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.playlist_name }}'
      - name: addsongtoplaylist
        template: addsongtoplaylist
        dependencies:
        - getuserid
        - playlistname2id
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: user_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.getuserid.result }}'
          - name: playlist_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.playlistname2id.result }}'
          - name: song_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.song_name }}'

  generateName: dependency-workflow-738-

      tasks:
      - name: getconcerts
        template: getconcerts
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: venue
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.venue }}'

      parameters:

      url: http://example.com/api/findtaxi
      method: GET
      parameters:
